name: Birb Seeb
description:
Birb Seeb

Our kakapo heroine must collect five seebs for her birbfriend.

But why are the seebs moving?!

We'll never know...

Credits

Special thanks to Coding in Flow for his excellent Unity 2D platformer tutorial series!

Made over the February 6, 2022, weekend for Mini Jam 99: Birds, which had the limitation "Can't stop moving."

Thank you for playing! Let me know if you enjoyed it in the comments!
